Feb 26, 2025
Release Notes
Introduced new parameter called "Minimum Distance for New Entry (%)". The aim is to reduce further the drawdown by assuring that new positions will be opened only at favorable price.
Feb 26, 2025
Release Notes
Added new parameter, called "Maximum Trade Duration (days)". The position will be closed either by exit condition, or after maximum trade duration days are reached.
Feb 26, 2025
Release Notes
Removed plot functionallity.
Mar 4, 2025
Release Notes
Updated the default account size value. Also introduced trade type: Long only, Short only, Long + Short. Added Moving Average as trend filter. Inside the source code you find the recommended settings for SPY and QQQ/NDQ
